{"tid":1322040,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"721宜日間遊行","createTime":"2019-07-15T23:56:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T13:42:33.000Z","uid":276633,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"70114c798f896e2e6ac72ba561308bbd75b51279","tid":1322040,"uid":276633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T23:56:27.000Z","msg":"就714沙田事件 一定會有更多市民支持我們的訴求<br />\n當中包括追究警方濫權及沙田新城市圍堵一事<br />\n定有更多市民願意站出來 支持大家<br />\n夜間集會 容易發生衝突 未必能夠讓大眾市民參與其中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為配合可以有更多人參與 <br />\n所以721應該要舉行日間遊行 讓人數再次破記錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n讓政府看見市民對政府 警方的不滿<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 非分化 完全黃絲<br />\n第一次出post 勿插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"761a018871afb4b99c2cbadba8dc34f7eb4e52eb","tid":1322040,"uid":64781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:18:57.000Z","msg":"「看見市民對政府 警方的不滿」<br />\n政府：oh I see<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bacbe523b1de3cc55a4981670cff2a054673df5","tid":1322040,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:20:05.000Z","msg":"睇到都當睇唔到架啦 要知一早知"},{"pid":"9a6f20bfb276f6ddda042532200bfcb5ba856453","tid":1322040,"uid":67197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:20:38.000Z","msg":"我覺得公民拘捕權支旗要整定<br />\n個日肯撚定又成萬個無編號既垃圾<br />\n我點解要比個睇唔到樣 全身裝備<br />\n但唔知佢係咪差佬既人驅趕甚至打"},{"pid":"ef26345e581fded271d7092f0f49c5ce13257334","tid":1322040,"uid":276633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"761a018871afb4b99c2cbadba8dc34f7eb4e52eb","tid":1322040,"uid":64781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:18:57.000Z","msg":"「看見市民對政府 警方的不滿」<br />\n政府：oh I see<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /